ISLAMABAD, Feb 01 (APP):Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib said on Tuesday that Prime Minister Imran Khan  during his visit to Bahawalpur today would present the gift of Sehat Insaf Card to 15 million population of Bahawalpur District, Rahim Yar Khan and Bahawalnagar in Bahawalpur Division.
In a tweet, he said that the PTI was the first government to provide free healthcare to every family up to Rs 1 million per year without any discrimination.
